query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q tq s) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('accelerometer',
'angular-dart',
'concat',
'currency',
'date-format',
'discord.py',
'do-while',
'netbeans-8',
'phonegap',
'preprocessor',
'profile',
'recursive-query',
'stylesheet',
'tcpdf',
'titanium-mobile');
